ation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic"}}}